Class FunctionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • Type
      • FunctionType

  • public class FunctionType
extends Type
    The type of a function is composed of a return type plus a list of types for its arguments (empty if none). It also has a field "prototype" indicating whether this represents a prototype declaration (without body) or a function definition (with body).

    MLB
